        "custom_liquid": "<section class=\"rr-section rr-section--paper rr-brand-hero\"><div class=\"rr-wrap rr-brand-hero__grid\"><div><div class=\"rr-eyebrow\">Root &amp; Route Creations Inc.</div><h1 class=\"rr-h1\">Uncovering the roots. Creating the routes.</h1><div class=\"rr-brand-hero__rule\"></div><div class=\"rr-subline\">Eco-luxury packaging for beauty, fragrance, and lifestyle brands.</div><p class=\"rr-intro\">Every product begins with an idea. Every idea begins with a story. We uncover the root beneath the brand, then design the route that carries it onto shelves, into homes, and into people's hearts.</p><div class=\"rr-brand-hero__actions\"><a class=\"rr-button\" href=\"/pages/contact\">Start an inquiry</a><a class=\"rr-button rr-button--secondary\" href=\"/pages/portfolio\">Explore portfolio</a></div></div><div class=\"rr-brand-hero__mark\"><svg width=\"112\" height=\"140\" viewBox=\"0 0 40 50\" fill=\"none\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 4 C9 12 9 27 20 34 C31 27 31 12 20 4 Z\" fill=\"currentColor\"/><path d=\"M20 20 V47\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.6\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/></svg></div></div></section>",
